channel.title: A bit ironic
channel.description: Well, I have read the threads about the comedy train(I was not actually there) but I find it ironic that 2 jagex staffs with gold crowns were there. I have thought this over and I think that the mods are all over this site. It's just a little TOO perfect that they knew exactly where to find the guys and their reaction time. I have been to plenty of these events in the past and no jagex mods are ever present. Which leads me to believe that jagex are looking over this stie with a fine-toothed comb. Too bad they are dumbasses and have no knowledge of programming, so they can't do much harm. But anyways, I think we should somehow find a way for getting jagex spies out of here, like banning all 0 posters after awhile. Post your opinion on how you think we should get rid of jagex staff/mods.
